<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">什么是</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring </span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架</span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">包括许多框架，例如</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring
                framework</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SpringMVC</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SpringBoot</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring Cloud</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring Data</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring Security
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">等。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64,"
        style="height:185px; width:632px"></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring framework
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">简称为</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架。</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架是全家桶内其它框架的基础和核心</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">由</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Rod Johnson
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">创立，</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">2004 </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">年发布了</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架的第一版，其目的是用于简化企业级应用程序开发的难度和周期。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">就是一个容器，以</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">xml</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签的形式管理对象，创建对象，给属性赋值</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Sring
            </span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架结构</span></strong></span>
</p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是分层的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Java SE/EE </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一站式轻量级开源框架</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64,"
        style="height:225px; width:225px"></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">以</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> IoC</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Inverse of
                Control</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，控制反转）和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> AOP</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Aspect Oriented
                Programming</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，面向切面编程）为内核。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64,"
        style="height:447px; width:579px"></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">IoC </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">指的是将对象的创建权交给</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">去创建。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">使用</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">之前，对象的创建都是由我们使用</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> new </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">创建，而使用</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">之后，对象的创建都交给了</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">用来封装多个类的公共行为，将那些与业务无关，却为业务模块所共同调用的逻辑封装起来，减少系统的重复代码，降低模块间的耦合度。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">另外，</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">还解决一些系统层面上的问题，比如日志、事务、权限等。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的特点</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架具有以下几个特点。</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">方便解耦，简化开发</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">就是一个大工厂，可以将所有对象的创建和依赖关系的维护交给</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">管理。</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">IoC</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">容器降低了业务对象替换的复杂性，提高了组件之间的解耦</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ORM</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DAO</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">提供了与第三方持久层框架的良好整合，并简化了底层的数据库访问</span></span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="2"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">方便集成各种优秀框架</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">不排斥各种优秀的开源框架，其内部提供了对各种优秀框架（如</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">
                        Struts2</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Hibernate</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">等）的直接支持。</span></span></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="3"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">降低</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Java EE API </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的使用难度</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的高度开放性，并不强制应用完全依赖于</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，开发者可自由选用</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架的部分或全部。</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Java EE
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">开发中非常难用的一些</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> API</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">（</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">JDBC</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">JavaMail</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、远程调用等）都提供了封装，使这些</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> API
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">应用的难度大大降低。</span></span></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="4"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">方便程序的测试</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">支持</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">
                        JUnit4</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，可以通过注解方便地测试</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">程序。</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">立于各种应用服务器，基于</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架的应用，可以真正实现</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Write
                        Once</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Run
                        Anywhere</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的承诺。</span></span></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="5"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">编程的支持</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">提供面向切面编程，可以方便地实现对程序进行权限拦截和运行监控等功能。</span></span>
            </li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">支持允许将一些通用任务如安全、事务、日志等进行集中式管理，从而提供了更好的复用。</span></span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="6"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">声明式事务的支持</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">只需要通过配置就可以完成对事务的管理，而无须手动编程。</span></span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ol>
